WEBVTT

00:00:29.885 --> 00:00:31.277
za njihove izloge.

00:00:31.277 --> 00:00:32.672
Ovaj se zove "Potjera".

00:00:32.672 --> 00:00:34.018
Dva su para cipela,

00:00:34.018 --> 00:00:35.643
muški i ženski par,

00:00:35.643 --> 00:00:38.547
i oni sudjeluju u ovoj polaganoj, 
napetoj potjeri,

00:00:38.547 --> 00:00:39.825
po izlogu

00:00:39.825 --> 00:00:42.050
u kojoj čovjek priđe ženi s leđa

00:00:42.050 --> 00:00:43.623
i uđe u njen osobni prostor,

00:00:43.623 --> 00:00:45.558
i onda se ona odmakne.

00:00:45.558 --> 00:00:47.399
Svaka cipela u sebi ima magnet,

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:49.402
i postoje magneti ispod stola

00:00:49.402 --> 00:00:51.366
koji pomiču cipele.

00:00:51.366 --> 00:00:53.398
Moj prijatelj Andy Cavatorta gradio je

00:00:53.398 --> 00:00:56.940
robotsku harfu za Biophilia turneju 
pjevačice Bjork,

00:00:56.940 --> 00:00:59.332
i ja sam radio elektroniku

00:00:59.332 --> 00:01:01.521
i softver za kontrolu kretanja